  "response": "While NIT Puducherry is a relatively younger institution compared to other National Institutes of Technology in India, it has started to gain recognition in recent years. As it is still building its reputation, there may not be many widely known or \"famous\" alumni yet. However, graduates from NIT Puducherry have gone on to pursue successful careers in various fields, including engineering, academia, and entrepreneurship.\n\nTypically, you would find alumni engaged in reputed companies, pursuing higher education at prestigious institutions, or contributing to research and technology innovation. For more specific names and achievements, it would be best to check the official NIT Puducherry alumni network or related social media groups where alumni share their accomplishments and career paths.",
